2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The proposed semi-supervised learning framework involves training a neural network, which falls under the domain of machine learning. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a novel approach to solve a computer vision problem, which can be considered as a subfield of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper deals with matching of images, which is a common task in multimedia analysis. 
5. cs.IR (Information Retrieval) - The paper proposes a method to match semantically related images, which can be useful in image retrieval applications.
